Sberbank May Buy Allianz Life Insurance Unit, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-13T05:51:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/sberbank-may-buy-allianz-life-insurance-unit-vedomosti-says.html
OAO Sberbank,  Russia ’s largest
bank, plans to buy a Russian life insurance business from
Allianz SE,  Vedomosti  reported, citing unidentified officials at
the bank and at the insurance company.  Sberbank hasn’t made a final decision, the newspaper said,
citing the bank official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
